;
SHEET
DETERMINATION METHOD: DSSP
THE SHEETS PRESENTED AS "AB" IN EACH CHAIN ON SHEET RECORDS
BELOW IS ACTUALLY AN  9-STRANDED BARREL THIS IS REPRESENTED BY
A 10-STRANDED SHEET IN WHICH THE FIRST AND LAST STRANDS
ARE IDENTICAL.

THE SHEETS PRESENTED AS "BB" IN EACH CHAIN ON SHEET RECORDS
BELOW IS ACTUALLY AN  9-STRANDED BARREL THIS IS REPRESENTED BY
A 10-STRANDED SHEET IN WHICH THE FIRST AND LAST STRANDS
ARE IDENTICAL.
;
